query:
UPDATE events SET 
  title = CASE id
    WHEN 1 THEN 'THE MIDNIGHT SESSION'
    WHEN 2 THEN 'CHAPTER INITIATION'
    WHEN 3 THEN 'UNDERGROUND COLLECTIVE'
    WHEN 4 THEN 'THE RITUAL'
    WHEN 5 THEN 'NEON NIGHTS'
    WHEN 6 THEN 'THE GATHERING'
    WHEN 7 THEN 'INNER CIRCLE ONLY'
    WHEN 8 THEN 'THE LAUNCH'
    ELSE title
  END,
  tagline = CASE id
    WHEN 1 THEN 'When the city sleeps, we gather'
    WHEN 2 THEN 'Your first step into the unknown'
    WHEN 3 THEN 'Where the real ones meet'
    WHEN 4 THEN 'A night you will never forget'
    WHEN 5 THEN 'Lights, sound, and pure energy'
    WHEN 6 THEN 'The collective assembles'
    WHEN 7 THEN 'For those who have earned it'
    WHEN 8 THEN 'The beginning of something new'
    ELSE tagline
  END,
  coverImageUrl = CASE id
    WHEN 1 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1470229722913-7c0e2dbbafd3?w=1920&q=80'
    WHEN 2 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1514525253161-7a46d19cd819?w=1920&q=80'
    WHEN 3 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571266028243-e4733b0f0bb0?w=1920&q=80'
    WHEN 4 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516450360452-9312f5e86fc7?w=1920&q=80'
    WHEN 5 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1574391884720-bbc3740c59d1?w=1920&q=80'
    WHEN 6 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1533174072545-7a4b6ad7a6c3?w=1920&q=80'
    WHEN 7 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1459749411175-04bf5292ceea?w=1920&q=80'
    WHEN 8 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1492684223066-81342ee5ff30?w=1920&q=80'
    ELSE coverImageUrl
  END,
  featuredOrder = CASE id
    WHEN 1 THEN 8
    WHEN 2 THEN 7
    WHEN 3 THEN 6
    WHEN 4 THEN 5
    WHEN 5 THEN 4
    WHEN 6 THEN 3
    WHEN 7 THEN 2
    WHEN 8 THEN 1
    ELSE featuredOrder
  END
WHERE id IN (1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8);
